Sigurno postoji neka priča iza toga.

485
00:38:56,416 --> 00:38:57,916
Što mislite, gospodine?

486
00:38:59,250 --> 00:39:00,916
O Deepaku?

487
00:39:01,875 --> 00:39:05,666
- Deepak je oženio tu djevojku.
-Što?

488
