499
00:39:55,625 --> 00:39:56,958
Hej, uzmi.

500
00:40:09,666 --> 00:40:10,791
sta to radis

501
00:40:11,708 --> 00:40:12,791
tražim

502
00:40:13,708 --> 00:40:16,250
