543
00:44:44,666 --> 00:44:46,083
Ram Ram, gospodine.

544
00:44:46,791 --> 00:44:47,750
Damodar.

545
00:44:48,791 --> 00:44:49,833
Da gospodine.

546
00:44:53,125 --> 00:44:54,541
poznajete li ga

547
